snippet: Lauren Silberman became the first woman to compete at an N.F.L. regional scouting combine but left the Jets’ practice field after reinjuring her quadriceps.
abstract: Lauren Silberman becomes first woman to compete at NFL regional scouting combine, but leaves New York Jets practice field after reinjuring her quadriceps.
lead_paragraph: Lauren Silberman became the first woman to compete at an N.F.L. regional scouting combine but left the Jets’ practice field after reinjuring her quadriceps.
